videos.headline: FIU scoop-and-score thanks to Charlotte fumble
videos.description: Charlotte RB Ishod Finger gets stuffed at the line and loses it, resulting in a scoop-and-score from FIU's Sage Lewis.

videos.headline: Maxwell finds edge and takes it all the way
videos.description: FIU RB Napoleon Maxwell follows a block and takes it to the house for a 39-yard touchdown.
